<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<html xmlns:MadCap="http://www.madcapsoftware.com/Schemas/MadCap.xsd">
    <body>
        <ol>
            <li>Open <span class="filepath">log4j.properties</span>, which can be found in your installation folder.</li>
            <li>Change the logging level. For example, increase the logging level by changing all three instances of <span class="code">info</span> to <span class="code">debug</span>. Which, when updated, should resemble:<ul><li><span class="code">log4j.logger.app=debug, app</span></li><li><span class="code">log4j.logger.access=debug, access</span></li><li><span class="code">log4j.rootLogger=debug, app, stdout</span></li></ul></li>
        </ol>
    </body>
</html>